methods.addSource:
Add a column location for consideration when constructing groupings.

:param columnLocation: (io.deephaven.db.v2.locations.ColumnLocation) - The column location to add
:param firstKey: (long) - The first key in the range for this column location
:param lastKey: (long) - The last key in the range for this column location (inclusive)

text:
Interface for GroupingProviders that operate on metadata derived from a ColumnLocation for a given
 Index key range.
